    "description": "<strong>Do You Like Sparklies?</strong><br><br>Raven Gold is a game founded on the concept of rewarding exploration. Explore handcrafted dungeons and find piles of hidden treasure<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067820/extras/screenshot7.PNG?t=1720396714\" /></span><br><br>Solve unique, challenging, handcrafted puzzles to find incredible treasure!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067820/extras/Screenshot4-1.PNG?t=1720396714\" /></span><br><br>But it's not just a casual stroll in the park! Face off with hordes of enemies! Use your wits to take on powerful bosses that have been carefully programmed with unique skills and behaviours!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067820/extras/Screenshot3-1.PNG?t=1720396714\" /></span><br><br>Once you've accrued some gold, decide what to do with it! Raven gold features a myriad of ways to spend your cash, from buying gear, to crafting, to buying key items that add to your experience!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067820/extras/Screenshot8-1.PNG?t=1720396714\" /></span><br><br>And if you're looking for an interesting story, there's one of those too!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067820/extras/Screenshot2-1.PNG?t=1720396714\" /></span>",
